    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 49-17-743, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT THE PUBLIC SERVICE COMMISSION SHALL NOT EFFECT A RULING, PROMULGATION, FINDING OR DECISION THAT INTERFERES OR CONFLICTS WITH THE POWERS GRANTED TO THE COUNTY AUTHORITY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
